        <release version="3.79.2" date="2020-12-18">
            <description>
                <p>What's new</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Gift cards</li>
                    <li>Update DOMPurify to 2.2.4</li>
                    <li>Show progress bar for loading calendar when initially accessing it</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Bugfixes:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Dialog for adding aliases does not redirect on "ok"</li>
                    <li>Too many empty lines between signature and email body</li>
                    <li>Do not load calendar events in parallel</li>
                    <li>Notification channel names are invalid</li>
                    <li>Do not restart SSE when new user is added</li>
                    <li>Quoted printable not supported for contact import</li>
                    <li>Improve colored text detection</li>
                    <li>MailViewer/MultMailViewer/MultiSearchViewer have different button positions</li>
                    <li>Weird behaviour of the Mail Editor</li>
                    <li>Failed assertion when reloading back in from settings view on firefox</li>
                    <li>Whitelabel 2FA form shows line 'more info' without link</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
        </release>
