        <release version="3.50.10" date="2019-04-25">
            <description>
                <p>New:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Enable white background for emails with colored text when dark theme is on</li>
                    <li>Hide attachments behind a spoiler when there are a lot of them</li>
                    <li>Make error dialog less annoying</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Bugfixes:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fixed indexing issues</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
        </release>
        <release version="3.50.1" date="2019-04-09">
            <description>
                <p>Bugfixes:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Prevent image loading destroys email layout (#1195)</li>
                    <li>We no longer bundle images that are b64 encoded (#1141)</li>
                    <li>Duplicate search results on Firefox (#1144)</li>
                </ul>
                <p>New:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Encrypt search index meta data (#711)</li>
                    <li>Improved search performance (#1142)</li>
                    <li>Improved performance when deleting folders (#837)</li>
                    <li>Improved send mail performance (#1161)</li>
                    <li>Automatic certificate provisioning for whitelabel domains (#252)</li>
                    <li>The desktop clients will now unhide all windows when a second instance is started instead of
                        quietly creating a new window. New windows can be created via Ctrl/Cmd+N or the tray icon menu
                        (#1186)
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </description>
